<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Hi</span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">To work in SA, it is mandatory to have a SA Working with Childrens Check and NDIS Check. Please see the below information on how to apply. <b>If you already have completed an NDIS Check and its current, <u><span style="color:red">do not</span></u> apply for a second one</b></span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"><a href="https://www.dcsiscreening.sa.gov.au/SCRequestApplicationIndividual" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">https://www.dcsiscreening.sa.gov.au/SCRequestApplicationIndividual</a></span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Once you have applied, you’ll receive an email from SA Health showing your application is in process. Please forward that through to us.</span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">When asked for an NDIS Employer ID, please use </span><b><span style="background:yellow"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">4-3LLK-1440</span></span></span></b></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><u><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Please let us know when you have completed your application</span></u></b><b><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">, as we need to approve it and don’t get notifications.</span></b></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><u><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:red">Failure to do this may result in your application being cancelled and losing money spent for the application.</span></span></u></b></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><u><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">PLEASE NOTE:</span></u></b><b><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"> You will not be able to start until at least one of the checks has cleared. </span></b><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">To help progress the application quicker, please call 1300 321 592 and email <a href="mailto:dhsscreeningunit@sa.gov.au" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">dhsscreeningunit@sa.gov.au</a> and let them know you require your checks cleared ASAP to begin work. It may also help to provide them with any other Working with Childrens Checks you have from other states. </span></span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><i><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">What you’ll need</span></span></i></b></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">100 point ID check</span></span></b></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">You will need to verify your identity as part of the application process.</span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">You can:</span></span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Verify your ID online, if you have:</span></span></span></span>

	<ul style="list-style-type:circle">
		<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 72.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">an Australian driver’s licence, and</span></span></span></span></li>
		<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 72.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">any one of these:</span></span></span></span>
		<ul style="list-style-type:square">
			<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 108.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Australian birth certificate</span></span></span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 108.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Australian passport</span></span></span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 108.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Australian citizenship certificate.</span></span></span></span></li>
		</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:115%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">If you can’t verify your identity online, Use the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.sa.gov.au/topics/rights-and-law/rights-and-responsibilities/screening-checks/apply-for-a-screening-check/print-and-seek" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline" title="Print and seek verification">Print and seek verification</a>&nbsp;option</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p>When you're ready, head over to the Alliance Portal to upload your documentation:</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;">
	
		<tr>
			<td align="center" bgcolor="#007DC3" style="background-color: #007DC3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;"><a href="https://allianceaustralia--uat.sandbox.my.salesforce-sites.com/onboarding/apex/b3o__MyDocuments?id={{{Recipient.Id}}}&amp;sessionKey={{{Recipient.Session_Key__c}}}" style="display: inline-block; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">OPEN THE ALLIANCE PORTAL</a></td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
<br />
<br />
Kind regards,&nbsp;<br />
Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</body>
</html>